data.title: Solar Turbines 2
data.meta_description: Solar Turbines 2 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Solar Turbines designs and manufactures rugged, reliable products using quality systems certified to ISO 9001 standards. The company has a fleet of more than 11,200 gas turbine units-with over 1,000,000,000 operating hours--installed in 90 nations. Solar gas turbines have low exhaust emissions levels and can meet virtually any current clean air standard with lean-premixed combustion technology.
